### ============================================
### 3. FORNECEDORES (MANAGER)
### ============================================

### 3.1 Criar fornecedor diretamente (MANAGER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers/direct
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_MANAGER_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "Fornecedor Teste Ltda",
  "cnpj": "11.111.111/0001-11",
  "email": "contato@fornecedorteste.com",
  "responsibleName": "João Silva"
}

### 3.2 Listar fornecedores (MANAGER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_MANAGER_AQUI

### ============================================
### 4. LOTES (MANAGER)
### ============================================

### 4.1 Criar lote (MANAGER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_MANAGER_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "batchId": "LOT-001",
  "productName": "Produto Teste",
  "quantity": 1000,
  "unit": "un"
}

### 4.2 Listar lotes (MANAGER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/batches
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_MANAGER_AQUI

### 4.3 Buscar lote específico (MANAGER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/batches/LOT-001
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_MANAGER_AQUI

### 4.4 Calcular CO2 do lote (MANAGER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches/LOT-001/calculate-co2
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_MANAGER_AQUI

### ============================================
### 5. DOCUMENTOS (SUPPLIER)
### ============================================

### 5.1 Upload de documento (FORNECEDOR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/upload
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_SUPPLIER_AQUI
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="batchId"

LOT-001
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="docType"

INVOICE
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="teste.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Este é um arquivo de teste
--boundary123--

### ============================================
### 6. PROCESSAR DOCUMENTOS (OPERATOR)
### ============================================

### 6.1 Ver documentos pendentes (OPERATOR)
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/pending
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_OPERATOR_AQUI

### ============================================
### 7. VALIDAR DOCUMENTOS (SPECIALIST)
### ============================================

### 7.1 Validar documento (SPECIALIST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/ID_DO_DOCUMENTO_AQUI/validate
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_SPECIALIST_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "extractedData": {
    "productName": "Produto Validado",
    "co2Emitted": 150,
    "supplier": "Fornecedor Teste"
  }
}

### ============================================
### 8. DASHBOARD
### ============================================

### 8.1 Dashboard da empresa (MANAGER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/companies/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_MANAGER_AQUI

